    "macroSummary": "US-Iran peace talks have collapsed with Trump threatening a Strait of Hormuz blockade, sending oil above $100 and triggering stagflation conditions while the dollar surges as a safe haven. Geopolitical risk premium is returning to markets with Bitcoin holding $70K but facing resistance, while traditional risk assets wobble under dual pressure from inflation fears and flight-to-quality flows.",
